quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  82,1,Sagbana yi ti cheei
  82,2,"Yaha! Saŋmarsi yi ti lu tiŋgbani ni, ka yaɣili luɣulikam"
  82,3,Yaha! Kulikara yi ti cheei kpe taba ni
  82,4,Yaha! Bɛ yi ti kurgi gbala
  82,5,"Nyɛvuli ni baŋ binshɛɣu di ni daŋsi, ni din naɣisi shɛli"
  82,6,Yaa nyini ninsala (chɛfura)! Bo n-leei yɔhim a n-zaŋ chaŋ a Duuma So Ŋun nam tibgila
  82,7,"Ŋuna n-nyɛ Ŋun nam a, ka pali a nama, ka nam a saɣisi"
  82,8,Ka O zaŋ a niŋ ŋmahiŋgbana shɛli ni O ni bɔra
  82,9,Haifa! Chɛli gba! Yi zaŋla sanyoo (Chiyaama dabsili) leei ʒiri
  82,10,Yaha! Achiika! Yi zuɣusaa mali (Malaaika shɛba) ban guli ya
  82,11,"Bɛ nyɛla ban mali jilma, ka nyɛla ban sabri yi tuuntumsa"
  82,12,Bɛ mila binshɛɣu yi ni niŋda
  82,13,Achiika! Naawuni dabsuma yɛn ti bela yolsigu puuni
  82,14,Achiika! Bibɛhi mi yɛn ti bela ʒehiimi (buɣum) puuni
  82,15,Ka bɛ yɛn ti kpe li Sanyoo- dali
  82,16,Bɛ mi pala ban yɛn tooi sɔɣi ka chɛ li
  82,17,"(Yaa nyini ŋun gbilsiri tibli)! Bo n-leei baŋsi a, bo n-leei nyɛ Sanyoodali"
  82,18,"Din nyaaŋa, bo n-leei baŋsi a din nyɛ Sanyoodali"
  82,19,"Dabsi’ shɛli nyɛvuli ni ti ka di nyɛvuli kpee yiko shɛli, dindali maa, yɛllikam daa yɛn ti nyɛla Naawuni ko dini"
  83,1,Azaaba kpeeni be ban filindi zaɣa (muuru bee sikeli) zuɣu
  83,2,"Bana n-nyɛ ninvuɣu shɛba ban yɛn zahim niriba sani, ka bɔri ni di pali"
  83,3,"Amaa! Bɛ yi ti yɛn zahim n-ti shɛba muuru ni bee sikeeli zuɣu, ka bɛ filinda"
  83,4,"Di ni bɔŋɔ, bannim’ maa bi tɛhiri ni bɛ nyɛla bɛ ni yɛn ti neei shɛba"
  83,5,Dabsi’ titali maa ni (Zaadali)
  83,6,Dabsi’ shɛli ninsalinim’ ni yɛn ti zani binnamda Duuma tooni